com.philips.pins.shinelib

Class SHNDeviceFoundInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.philips.pins.shinelib.SHNDeviceFoundInfo

  • public class SHNDeviceFoundInfo
extends Object
    SHNDeviceFoundInfo contains information obtained from the peripheral during scanning.

    SHNDeviceFoundInfo is returned by SHNDeviceScanner.
